The Permanent Secretary, State House, Jalal Arabi, has urged the public to ignore notices of recruitment at State House Clinic currently making the rounds on the internet. The Permanent Secretary, in a statement by the Deputy Director, Information, Attah Esa, advised the public to be more circumspect and wary of such notices that are designed by mischief makers to deceive and extort unsuspecting job seekers. Arabi assured that the sponsors of the publication will be investigated and prosecuted.